    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="671055257">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-671055257" class="vote-count">3</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-671055257" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="671055257">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/heqiu/">書蠹</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar40 rating" title="推荐"></span>
                    <span>2013-04-28</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">《正韓》是熊先生為本朝太祖極權主義辯護的一篇妙文，他雖知極權主義之害處，卻認為適當的集權是有益國家的，但後果卻是沒有人能保持住“適當”二字</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="492469814">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-492469814" class="vote-count">1</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-492469814" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="492469814">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/leoyin1989/">白鹇</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar50 rating" title="力荐"></span>
                    <span>2012-03-29</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">刘小枫把熊十力在《正韩》（即韩非子评论）里的观点概括为提倡“圣人独裁”，真是大谬。刘自己要搞法西斯主义，结果把别人也看做法西斯主义者。</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="760893949">
